      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, the car is in perfect working order, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Every feature, from the advanced electronics to the smooth-shifting transmission, functions exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives like it is brand new.",
